subject: Economy
question_en: What is the Gross Domestic Product (GDP) of Rajasthan in Rs. Millions for the year 2019-2020?
question_hi: राजस्थान के वर्ष 2019-2020 के दरवाज़े में ग्रॉस डोमेन प्रणाम (GDP) क्या है।
explanation_en: According to the National Institute of Statistics of India, the Gross Domestic Product (GDP) of Rajasthan at Current Market Prices for the year 2019-2020 is Rs. 98,390 crore.
